name: BodyFatCalculator
0:
”Alexa, open fat calculator”
”Alexa, ask fat calculator to calculate it”
”Alexa, ask fat calculator about my fat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fat calculator
des:
Now you can calculate percent of your body fat with this alexa skill!

Enable it and know your %. If you have goal to make it higher or lower you can always ask alexa to calculate it. Also have fun to know your friends body fat percent.

For the future we will implement diet meals for those who would be interested to make % lower or higher.

This Body Fat Calculator uses the U.S. Navy fitness formula to get an estimated measuring of body fat percent. Use a tape measure then tell your waist, hip(If your a female), neck and height measurements to get the result!

HAPPY COUNTING!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
